  "mainHtml": "\n<section class=\"page-hero industry\">\n<div class=\"container hero-inner\">\n<div class=\"hero-copy\">\n<h1>行业精密制造方案</h1>\n<p>面向重点行业的结构件、功能件、夹具和样件需求，提供材料、工艺、检测和交付配套。</p>\n<div class=\"hero-stats\">\n<div class=\"hero-stat\"><strong>9类</strong><span>重点行业</span></div>\n<div class=\"hero-stat\"><strong>方案+案例</strong><span>按行业沉淀</span></div>\n<div class=\"hero-stat\"><strong>样件-小批量</strong><span>持续交付</span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section industry-category-section\">\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div class=\"section-head industry-section-head\">\n<h2>行业分类</h2>\n<p>不同领域对应不同的零件功能、材料选择、检测重点和交付节奏。</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"industry-category-grid\">\n<article class=\"industry-category-card\">\n<img alt=\"航天行业制造\" src=\"/precision/Aerospace.jpg\"/>\n<div>\n<span>高可靠装备</span>\n<h3>航天</h3>\n<p>承力结构 / 薄壁腔体 / 高强连接</p>\n<div class=\"category-tags\"><b>五轴加工、铝/钛合金加工、CMM检测、首件资料</b></div>\n<a class=\"text-link\" href=\"/industries/aerospace\">进入航天行业</a>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"industry-category-card\">\n<img alt=\"医疗器械行业制造\" src=\"/precision/Medical_devices.jpg\"/>\n<div>\n<span>高可靠装备</span>\n<h3>医疗器械</h3>\n<p>设备部件 / 测试夹具 / 非植入结构件</p>\n<div class=\"category-tags\"><b>CNC精密加工、工程塑料加工、不锈钢加工、尺寸报告</b></div>\n<a class=\"text-link\" href=\"/industries/medical\">进入医疗器械行业</a>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"industry-category-card\">\n<img alt=\"汽车行业制造\" src=\"/precision/industry-auto-engine.jpg\"/>\n<div>\n<span>批量验证</span>\n<h3>汽车</h3>\n<p>装配验证 / 强度验证 / 试产准备</p>\n<div class=\"category-tags\"><b>CNC、钣金、表面处理、装配校准</b></div>\n<a class=\"text-link\" href=\"/industries/automotive\">进入汽车行业</a>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"industry-category-card\">\n<img alt=\"机器人技术行业制造\" src=\"/precision/Industrial_Automation.jpg\"/>\n<div>\n<span>批量验证</span>\n<h3>机器人技术</h3>\n<p>运动结构 / 快换接口 / 重复定位</p>\n<div class=\"category-tags\"><b>铝合金加工、硬质阳极、孔位检测、装配复核</b></div>\n<a class=\"text-link\" href=\"/industries/robotics\">进入机器人技术行业</a>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"industry-category-card\">\n<img alt=\"电子行业制造\" src=\"/precision/industry-electronics-pcb.jpg\"/>\n<div>\n<span>产品结构</span>\n<h3>电子</h3>\n<p>散热 / 接口 / 外观样机</p>\n<div class=\"category-tags\"><b>CNC加工、喷砂阳极、接口孔检测、外观处理</b></div>\n<a class=\"text-link\" href=\"/industries/electronics\">进入电子行业</a>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"industry-category-card\">\n<img alt=\"通信行业制造\" src=\"/precision/Equipment-Technology-Introduction.jpg\"/>\n<div>\n<span>批量验证</span>\n<h3>通信</h3>\n<p>屏蔽 / 耐候 / 设备装配</p>\n<div class=\"category-tags\"><b>铝合金加工、喷涂、电镀、密封面检测</b></div>\n<a class=\"text-link\" href=\"/industries/telecom\">进入通信行业</a>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"industry-category-card\">\n<img alt=\"半导体行业制造\" src=\"/precision/industry-semiconductor-wafer.jpg\"/>\n<div>\n<span>高可靠装备</span>\n<h3>半导体</h3>\n<p>基准定位 / 检测治具 / 备件加工</p>\n<div class=\"category-tags\"><b>精密CNC、洁净包装、平面度检测、批次追溯</b></div>\n<a class=\"text-link\" href=\"/industries/semiconductor\">进入半导体行业</a>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"industry-category-card\">\n<img alt=\"新能源行业制造\" src=\"/precision/new_energy.jpg\"/>\n<div>\n<span>批量验证</span>\n<h3>新能源</h3>\n<p>散热 / 绝缘 / 定位压紧</p>\n<div class=\"category-tags\"><b>铝合金加工、工程塑料加工、表面处理、装配验证</b></div>\n<a class=\"text-link\" href=\"/industries/new-energy\">进入新能源行业</a>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"industry-category-card\">\n<img alt=\"消费品行业制造\" src=\"/precision/industry-consumer-smartwatch.jpg\"/>\n<div>\n<span>产品结构</span>\n<h3>消费品</h3>\n<p>外观展示 / 装配验证 / 试制迭代</p>\n<div class=\"category-tags\"><b>CNC、3D打印、喷涂、阳极、抛光</b></div>\n<a class=\"text-link\" href=\"/industries/consumer\">进入消费品行业</a>\n</div>\n</article>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section soft case-library-section\" id=\"case-library\">\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div class=\"section-head industry-section-head\">\n<h2>行业案例库</h2>\n<p>汇总各行业案例，按行业、零件功能和制造关键词快速定位。</p>\n</div>\n<div aria-label=\"行业案例筛选\" class=\"case-library-tools\">\n<label class=\"case-search-field\">\n<span>关键词</span>\n<input autocomplete=\"off\" id=\"caseSearch\" placeholder=\"搜索行业、零件、工艺、材料\" type=\"search\"/>\n</label>\n<div aria-label=\"行业筛选\" class=\"case-filter-group\" id=\"caseIndustryFilters\">\n<button class=\"is-active\" data-industry=\"all\" type=\"button\">全部行业</button>\n<button data-industry=\"航天\" type=\"button\">航天</button>\n<button data-industry=\"医疗器械\" type=\"button\">医疗器械</button>\n<button data-industry=\"汽车\" type=\"button\">汽车</button>\n<button data-industry=\"机器人技术\" type=\"button\">机器人技术</button>\n<button data-industry=\"电子\" type=\"button\">电子</button>\n<button data-industry=\"通信\" type=\"button\">通信</button>\n<button data-industry=\"半导体\" type=\"button\">半导体</button>\n<button data-industry=\"新能源\" type=\"button\">新能源</button>\n<button data-industry=\"消费品\" type=\"button\">消费品</button>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"case-library-status\">\n<span id=\"caseResultCount\"></span>\n<button id=\"caseReset\" type=\"button\">重置筛选</button>\n</div>\n<div class=\"case-library-grid\" id=\"caseLibraryGrid\"></div>\n<div aria-label=\"案例分页\" class=\"case-pagination\" id=\"casePagination\">\n<button id=\"casePrev\" type=\"button\">上一页</button>\n<span id=\"casePageInfo\"></span>\n<button id=\"caseNext\" type=\"button\">下一页</button>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"cta-band\">\n<div class=\"container cta-inner\">\n<div><h2>需要匹配行业制造方案？</h2><p>上传图纸、模型或应用场景，我们会结合零件功能、材料、工艺和检测资料评估交付方案。</p></div>\n<a class=\"light-btn\" href=\"/quote?mode=quickQuote#quote-upload\">立即报价</a>\n</div>\n</section>\n"
